column1: #Text=Both suspects in the death of Savanna Greywind have entered not guilty pleas in court in Fargo , North Dakota , United States .
#Text=On Tuesday , William Hoehn , acting through his lawyer , pled not guilty to counts of conspiracy to commit murder , kidnapping , and giving false information to the police .
#Text=On Thursday , his girlfriend Brooke Crews did the same , procedurally .
#Text=Hoehn 's next hearing is scheduled for December and Crews ' for January .
